{"tid":783398,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳意涵七夕閃婚：寶寶快四月大了","createTime":"2018-08-17T13:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T11:22:33.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9488629914b5440949a3073ba9809ce36bb97718","tid":783398,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"前天才對外宣布懷孕4個月，今(17)天七夕情人節與導演男友許富翔在木柵登記結婚，結婚喜悅表露無遺，也為演藝圈投下震撼彈。她15日在社群網站證實喜訊：「是的，人生下一篇章，就這樣開啟了，謝謝你們的祝福，我很幸福哦！」<br />\n<br />\n今早戶政事務所聚集大批媒體，小倆口似乎也早有準備，現身時表現得一派輕鬆，過程只花了30-40分鐘。陳意涵表示，她一直都很想當媽媽，不會感到緊張，「你們（媒體）這樣我比較緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n日前蘋果拍到陳意涵小腹微凸，疑似懷孕，不過她先對外闢謠說，「沒有這回事」，近日又爆出懷孕消息後，今晚親自在臉書俏皮寫下：「吼⋯ 都計畫好情人節登記完就要告訴你們的，被搶先一步了，有一種自己的禮物被別人先打開的感覺哈哈 （好險禮物還是我的）」但她認為「不論如何，一切都是美好且珍惜的，是的，人生下一篇章就這樣開啟了，謝謝你們的祝福，我很幸福哦」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/j1erO2Q_PeGP1_Wnen7cIQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ch5z_VwDttxR5kpDD52.4g--~B/aD0zNDA7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/dc31f0ceeed516028fd023087b99fc97\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fj1erO2Q_PeGP1_Wnen7cIQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fch5z_VwDttxR5kpDD52.4g--~B%2FaD0zNDA7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fdc31f0ceeed516028fd023087b99fc97&h=a7868267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/K9ydQzoa.zOTQx3iywhgWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4xNTY4NjI3NDUwOTgwNw--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Aoausr4TmU9QsX0NXpdsmw--~B/aD0yODc7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/5890e14e6f32aa9a69cf53ba25ad4345\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FK9ydQzoa.zOTQx3iyw